ygData.messageBody:
If you just need netted, you may want to try the froglocks in the Qeynos
sewers. They occasionally have netted. The three I found are underwater
near the entrance by the Bank.

Jason

-----Original Message-----
From: Steve Heath [SMTP:stephenheath@...]
Sent: Tuesday, June 22, 1999 1:10 PM
To: EQ-Monks@onelist.com
Subject: Re: [EQ-Monks] MESH / NETTED ARMOUR

From: "Steve Heath" <stephenheath@...>

Have you headed down to innothule (sp?) swamp? Even if you can't find it
yourself, I've often come across trolls who will sell it (albeit for high
prices). Still, considering in Qeynos someone would have been happy to pay
12pp for netted gloves, it's probably worth the trip.
